<seg id=1> The Irish Republican Army announces the cease-fire </seg>
</hl> 
<p> 
<seg id=2> The New China News Agency London on August 31st news (Reporter the Li article is vast) the Irish Republican Army today announces, from today midnight, this organization thoroughly will stop all military activities, the implementation " unconditionally and not by a set time " the cease-fire. </seg>
</p> 
<p> 
<seg id=3> The Irish Republican Army said in one to English and in the Irish news media publication statement, considers the current situation and in order to advance the Northern Ireland peace advancement, this organization made the above decision, and informed this decision its subordinate's all armies. </seg>
</p> 
<p> 
<seg id=4> The statement requests the responsibility which the English government faces up to oneself undertakes, will urge related all quarters by to be firm and the patience facing the new situation which will bring by this cease-fire, holds widespread negotiations which will participate by English and the Irish government as well as Northern Ireland each main political party, finally will solve Northern Ireland's conflict. </seg>
</p> 
<p> 
<seg id=5> The statement said, the Irish Republican Army announces the cease-fire, " fair and the permanent solution " provided the opportunity for the Northern Ireland question. </seg>
<seg id=6> But the Irish Republican Army also reiterates, it still will abide by it " the republican goal ", namely Irish entire island unification. </seg>
</p> 
<p> 
<seg id=7> In order to realize Northern Ireland and Republic of Ireland's unification, the Irish Republican Army has carried on in Northern Ireland 25 years violence activity. </seg>
</p> 
